<ls>Ms. 7. 185.</ls>

{@--9@} A termination added to
nouns and adjectives in the sense of
‘a little less than,’ ‘almost like,’
‘nearly equal to,’ (denoting 
similarity with a degree of inferiority);
{#kumArakalpaM suzuve kumAraM#} <ls>R. 5. 36</ls>;
{#upapannametadasminnfzikalpe rAjani#} <ls>Ś. 2</ls>;
